{"type":null,"faqId":20992,"title":"如何启用PIN码锁定屏幕？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span class=\"s2\">设置&gt;隐身和安全&gt;安全&gt;加密&gt;加密手机&gt;PIN</span><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s2\">选择你的PIN”</span><span>下面的提示框中输入PIN码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>再次输入刚才输入的PIN码，点击</span><span class=\"s2\">确定</span><span>完成对PIN码的设定。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入PIN码解锁界面，输入设定的PIN码后点击“</span><span class=\"s2\">OK</span><span>”解除PIN码的锁定。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4655","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426837635000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-CL10,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":60,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}